entries.journal_entry_description: A shuttle carrying research equipment was shot down just outside of Dee'ja Peak upon its arrival. Go to the crash site and salvage as much of the equipment as you can.
entries.journal_entry_title: Salvage the Equipment at the Crashed Shuttle
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Defeating rabid narglatch matriarchs around the crashed shuttle.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Defeat rabid narglatches around the crashed shuttle.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Help clear the area around the crashed shuttle by removing some of the rabid narglatches from the area.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: The rabid narglatch known as Grizzlefur stalks the region in which the shuttle crashed. You should eliminate Grizzlefur so that he does not pose a threat.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Salvage as much research equipment from the crash site as is possible.
entries.task05_journal_entry_title: Salvage Research Equipment from the Crash Site
entries.task06_message_box_text: The last crate was empty. It looks like it was opened by someone, and since there is no sign of its contents, that someone must have taken whatever was inside. On the ground next to the crate is a torn bit of cloth with the Darkwalker symbol on it.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Return to Tanoa Vills with the research equipment and let her know about the empty crate.
